---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contribute"
  description="How to contribute expertise, review chapters, or suggest edits to the Democracy 2028 framework."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1>Contribute to Democracy 2028</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      This framework is only as good as the people who build it. We need policy experts,
      researchers, practitioners, fact-checkers, and engaged citizens.
    </p>

    <div class="ways-grid">
      <div class="way-card">
        <span class="way-icon">&#9997;&#65039;</span>
        <h2>Author a Chapter</h2>
        <p>
          We are seeking subject-matter experts to author chapters in their area.
          Each chapter follows a standard template and goes through peer review.
          See the full list of chapters needing authors on the{' '}
          <a href="/framework">Framework page</a>.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/democracyproject2028/democracyproject2028/issues/new?template=chapter-proposal.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta-link">
          Propose a chapter &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="way-card">
        <span class="way-icon">&#128270;</span>
        <h2>Fact-Check &amp; Review</h2>
        <p>
          Read published chapters and flag factual errors, outdated information,
          missing perspectives, or sources that need verification. Use GitHub issues
          to submit corrections.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/democracyproject2028/democracyproject2028/issues/new?template=fact-check.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta-link">
          Flag an issue &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="way-card">
        <span class="way-icon">&#128204;</span>
        <h2>Suggest Policy</h2>
        <p>
          Have a specific policy recommendation, case study, or piece of research
          you think should be incorporated? Open an issue and make the case.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/democracyproject2028/democracyproject2028/issues/new?template=policy-suggestion.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta-link">
          Suggest a policy &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Contribution Standards</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Every factual claim must have a source (peer-reviewed research preferred)</li>
      <li>Tone: authoritative but accessible — write for an intelligent general reader</li>
      <li>Acknowledge complexity and trade-offs honestly</li>
      <li>When discussing Project 2025 proposals, be factual and fair before critical</li>
      <li>Minimum 15 sources per chapter; target 30+</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      See the full{' '}
      <a href="https://github.com/democracyproject2028/democracyproject2028/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        contribution guidelines on GitHub
      </a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-slate);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .ways-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .way-card {
    background: var(--color-warm-gray);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
  }

  .way-icon { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }

  p, li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #374151;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  a { color: var(--color-navy); }
  a:hover { color: var(--color-gold); }

  .cta-link {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
